{"tid":531901,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"兩超市女職員有積怨 觸發廁所大戰","createTime":"2018-01-17T09:34:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-17T09:44:10.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9dac6af6ca613f67962899466991bba630451e5a","tid":531901,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T09:34:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180117/20277282\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180117%2F20277282&d=sRCflz5w7axcw7q5tLSXsQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=242fb49d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180117%2F20277282&h=3dbaefee\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180117/20277282</a><br />\n<br />\n兩超市女職員有積怨<br />\n觸發廁所大戰<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n0:00<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】金鐘太古廣場地庫一間超級市場，昨晨1時許，兩名素有積怨的超市女職員，工作期間起爭執，初則口角繼而動武，拳腳互毆。警員接報到場調查，兩女職員均受輕傷，事後一併送院治理。警方調查後，姓盧女職員(35歲)涉嫌襲擊致造成實際身體傷害，姓周女職員(46歲)涉嫌普通襲擊，一併被捕調查。"},{"pid":"140e9015b10b8520ce083fe925b3a4d418dc5a2d","tid":531901,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T09:37:00.000Z","msg":"通常互毆兩敗俱輕傷唔係和解嘅咩？"},{"pid":"31235828f46d434706f8f04fd8f58d1978546cbe","tid":531901,"uid":4917,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T09:38:31.000Z","msg":"姓關？"},{"pid":"4f49857a5ac3514434b2a911355f88a3fb3d0b42","tid":531901,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T09:41:06.000Z","msg":"仲以為係APITA vs AEON <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89273aaa661f9fce8539c0cb9381e8c9729dda2c","tid":531901,"uid":99805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"140e9015b10b8520ce083fe925b3a4d418dc5a2d","tid":531901,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T09: